{"tid":2431115,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"被控管鐵棒圖破壞支旅社  青年遭還押3個月今認罪","createTime":"2021-03-03T11:52:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T14:06:11.000Z","uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7046456034bfca5daf7b92d5009a4e1189626ef8","tid":2431115,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T11:52:04.000Z","msg":"前年10月初街頭示威持續，有少年凌晨時分在旺角手持鐵棒，打算破壞中旅社分店，被警察追捕制服。少年原本被控在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器罪，控方及後修訂控罪，少年今在西九龍法院承認管有物品意圖摧毀財產罪。裁判官香淑嫻押後至本月17日判刑，等候索取被告的<span class=\"red\">背景報告及勞教中心、教導所、更生中心報告</span>。<br />\n<br />\n現年18歲的被告李原本獲准保釋，<span class=\"red\">惟早前因晚上外出踩單車而違反宵禁令，擔保遭撤銷，至今已還柙3個月</span>。他干犯本案時有其他不同類案件的守行為命令在身，辯方大律師坦言，被告守法意識也許不強，但還柙令他有機會反省，被告已有悔意。"},{"pid":"6fbcbf217aba838e13e4ab65cf63fdb904e3c96e","tid":2431115,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T11:52:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210303/R4NDKFQONVBEJLCATJRE6EK3QQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210303%2FR4NDKFQONVBEJLCATJRE6EK3QQ%2F&d=UjOWczzRfTNgHoC3e3JiXwTszQqcSrFeuHGFn5Djw6E%3D&h=70237b3f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210303%2FR4NDKFQONVBEJLCATJRE6EK3QQ%2F&h=a37e55d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210303/R4NDKFQONVBEJLCATJRE6EK3QQ/</a>"},{"pid":"21bcf07246cd0cb1ab1ff0e04d2022dc1a49b336","tid":2431115,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T11:57:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22693a95b4f5d3d90e532c1c75bc40b257478f53","tid":2431115,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T12:03:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ff3744ed182e7bb30b146e2a04096284eb9dc96","tid":2431115,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T12:04:53.000Z","